  "title": "Junior Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p>Our Junior QS is based at our workshop at Admiralty. This dynamic role is working closely with the ID/Construction arms.</p><ul><li><p>Assist in preparing and reviewing project requirements, cost estimates, and procurement schedules.</p></li><li><p>Support the sourcing and evaluation of quotations from suppliers and subcontractors.</p></li><li><p>Assist in procurement of materials and subcontractor packages as per project requirements.</p></li><li><p>Monitor project budgets and costs under guidance, and help identify cost variations.</p></li><li><p>Support contract administration tasks, including progress claims and payment certifications.</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate and organized documentation of contracts, quotations, and procurement records.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with internal teams, suppliers, and subcontractors to facilitate smooth project progress.</p></li><li><p>Ensure work is carried out in compliance with company policies and relevant industry standards.</p></li><li><p>Undertake general and finance administration duties.</p></li><li><p>Perform other ad hoc duties assigned by supervisors.</p></li></ul><p><br />\n\n</p>",
