    "description": "<p>Brandsbridge Pte Ltd assists our clients in staying ahead in their business by providing impactful services in interior design, build, IT solutions and visual merchandising props.We emphasize providing services which create business impact to our clients, high quality craftsmanship, on-time and on-budget. The Company mainly serves retail and commercial clients.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are now part of a leading construction company in Singapore, Lum Chang group, and is known as LUM CHANG BRANDSBRIDGE PTE LTD. This helps us to tap with the best practice with more than 70 years in the industry.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We believe that everyone in Brandsbridge must excel. We value self-development, career progress and most importantly a healthy working culture.</p>",
